I2, I1, A, B = table.unpack(({ {3.624e-6, 2.691e-3, 2.987e-2, 0.1433}, {3.363e-6, 2.497e-3, 2.972e-2, 0.1452} })[property.getNumber('Car Type')])
SQRT3 = math.sqrt(3) min, max = math.min, math.max function clamp(x, a, b) return min(max(x, a), b) end
gB, gN = input.getBool, input.getNumber function gI(c) return math.floor(gN(c)) end
function onTick() eb = gB(1) brake_step, power_step, direction, dynamic_brake = gI(1), gI(2), gI(3), gI(4) v_sign, speed_ms = gN(5) > 0 and 1 or -1, gN(6) decel, accel = gN(7), gN(8)
speed_kph = 3.6*speed_ms
decel_t = -0.112*brake_step if eb then decel_t = -4.8 end accel_t = 0 if power_step >= 4 then accel_t = min(3, min(115/speed_kph, (107/speed_kph)^2)) elseif power_step >= 3 then accel_t = min(3, (115/SQRT3/speed_kph)^2) elseif power_step >= 2 then accel_t = min(2, (115/2/SQRT3/speed_kph)^2) elseif power_step >= 1 then accel_t = min(1, (4/speed_kph)^2) end accel_t = direction*accel_t if eb then accel_t = 0 end drag = -0.1*speed_ms/35
regen = (dynamic_brake >> 2 & 1) * clamp((speed_kph - 0.5)/4, 0, 1) if eb then regen = 0 end brake_pressure = max(-100*decel*(1 - regen), 0) motor_current = 100*(direction*accel + decel*regen)
brake = clamp(-B*decel/max(speed_ms, 0.1), 0, 1) if brake < 0.011 then brake = 0 accel = accel + decel end throttle = clamp(v_sign*(I2*speed_ms^2 + I1*speed_ms) + A*(accel + direction*drag)/3.6, -1, 1)
output.setNumber(1, brake) output.setNumber(2, throttle) output.setNumber(3, brake_pressure) output.setNumber(4, motor_current) output.setNumber(5, decel) output.setNumber(6, accel) output.setNumber(7, speed_ms) output.setNumber(31, decel_t) output.setNumber(32, accel_t) end

M, S = math, screen abs, floor, cos, pi = M.abs, M.floor, M.cos, M.pi function round(x) return floor(x + 0.5) end function fpart(x) return x - floor(x) end function rfpart(x) return 1 - fpart(x) end function clamp(x,a,b)return M.min(M.max(x,a),b)end
theme_l = {{7, 7, 7}} theme_d = {{130, 130, 130}} theme = theme_l
gB, gN = input.getBool, input.getNumber
key, speed, bc_prs, mr_prs, voltage, current, clock = false, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0 function onTick() theme = gB(1) and theme_d or theme_l key = gB(2) speed = gN(1) * 3.6 bc_prs, mr_prs = gN(2), gN(3) voltage, current = gN(4), gN(5) clock = gN(6) end
function C(c,o)S.setColor(c[1],c[2],c[3],o or 255)end function R(x,y,w,h)S.drawRectF(x,y,w,h)end function V(x,y,h)R(x,y,1,h)end function H(x,y,w)R(x,y,w,1)end function D(x,y)H(x,y,1)end
function drawLine(x0, y0, x1, y1, rgb) steep = abs(y1 - y0) > abs(x1 - x0)
function plot(x, y, c) if steep then x, y = y, x end C(rgb, 255 * (1 - cos(c * pi)) / 2) D(x, y) end
if steep then x0, y0 = y0, x0 x1, y1 = y1, x1 end if x0 > x1 then x0, x1 = x1, x0 y0, y1 = y1, y0 end
dx = x1 - x0 dy = y1 - y0
if dx == 0.0 then gradient = 1.0 else gradient = dy / dx end
xend = round(x0) yend = y0 + gradient * (xend - x0) xgap = rfpart(x0 + 0.5) xpxl1 = xend ypxl1 = floor(yend) plot(xpxl1, ypxl1 , rfpart(yend) * xgap) plot(xpxl1, ypxl1+1, fpart(yend) * xgap) intery = yend + gradient
xend = round(x1) yend = y1 + gradient * (xend - x1) xgap = fpart(x1 + 0.5) xpxl2 = xend ypxl2 = floor(yend) plot(xpxl2, ypxl2, rfpart(yend) * xgap) plot(xpxl2, ypxl2+1, fpart(yend) * xgap)
for x = xpxl1 + 1, xpxl2 - 1 do plot(x, floor(intery), rfpart(intery)) plot(x, floor(intery)+1, fpart(intery)) intery = intery + gradient end end
function draw_needle(x, y, r, theta, rgb) theta = theta / 180 * pi drawLine(x, y, x + r * math.sin(theta), y - r * cos(theta), rgb) end
function draw_number(x,y,v,w,c,z,d) d=d or 0 v=clamp(M.floor(10^d*v+0.5),0,10^w-1) x=x+4*w-4 for i=1,w do n=v%10 if i==d then C(c,127) D(x-1,y+4) end if v~=0 or z or i<=d+1 then C(c) if n==0 or 4<=n and n~=7 then V(x,y,3) end if n%2==0 and n~=4 then V(x,y+2,3) end if n~=1 and n~=4 then H(x,y,3) end if 2<=n and n~=7 then H(x,y+2,3) end if n~=1 and n~=4 and n~=7 then H(x,y+4,3) end if n~=5 and n~=6 then V(x+2,y,3) end if n~=2 then V(x+2,y+2,3) end end v=v//10 x=x-4 end end
function onDraw() draw_number(51,21,speed,3,theme[1]) draw_needle(57, 15, 11, -126 + 1.8 * speed, theme[1]) draw_needle(32, 20, 8, -135 + 0.27 * bc_prs, theme[1]) draw_needle(32, 20, 8, -135 + 0.27 * mr_prs, {77, 8, 8}) draw_needle(14, 8, 5, -150 + 0.1 * voltage, theme[1]) draw_needle(14, 23, 5, 0.24 * current, theme[1]) C(theme[1])V(14,8,1)V(14,23,1)H(31,20,3)V(32,19,3)H(56,15,3)V(57,14,3) if key then C({26,30,36})R(82,25,7,3)R(83,24,5,5)R(84,23,3,7)C({113,113,113})R(83,25,5,3)R(84,24,3,5) draw_needle(85, 26, 2.5, 720 * 12 * clock, {40, 40, 40}) draw_needle(85, 26, 2, 720 * clock, {7, 7, 7}) end end

S=screen R=S.drawRectF function C(c)S.setColor(c[1],c[2],c[3])end function V(x,y,h)R(x,y,1,h)end function H(x,y,w)R(x,y,w,1)end function D(x,y)V(x,y,1)end
function draw_a(x,y)V(x,y+1,3)D(x+1,y)D(x+1,y+2)V(x+2,y+1,3)end function draw_c(x,y)V(x,y+1,2)D(x+1,y)D(x+1,y+3)end function draw_o(x,y)draw_c(x,y)V(x+2,y+1,2)end function draw_s(x,y)D(x+1,y)D(x,y+1)D(x+1,y+2)D(x,y+3)end function draw_t(x,y)H(x,y,3)V(x+1,y+1,3)end

for i=notice_speed//5,aspect_speed//5 do p=ATC_SPD_IND[i+1] if p then C(i==0 and COLORS.red or COLORS.green) D(p[1],p[2]) end end end
if tasc_ready then C(COLORS.green) draw_t(34,1)draw_a(37,1)draw_s(40,1)draw_c(43,1) end
if ats_active then C(COLORS.green) draw_a(23,6)draw_t(26,6)draw_s(29,6) end

-- VVVF Controller by Nona Takahara MASS_M_CAR = 35 -- Mg (t) UNIT_CURRENT_MAX_P = 720 -- A UNIT_CURRENT_MAX_B = 1200 -- A REG_BRAKE = false MOTOR_PER_UNIT = 4 -- Number of motors(REAL) controlled from this microcontroller(SW) CONST_VF = 0.0256 -- V/f constant V/(km/h) BOOST = 1.25
MAX_LINE_VOLTAGE = 1.82 -- kV REFINE_VOLTAGE = 1.70 -- kV LINE_VOLTAGE_LPF = 0.1
_CONS=false function TargetCurrent(notch, unitMass, velocity, cv, boost) local vfcCurrent, maxCurrent, slipMaxSpdAtMaxC = 0, 0, 100 local bsk = boost and BOOST or 1 if notch == 1 then vfcCurrent = 0.5 maxCurrent = 0.5 slipMaxSpdAtMaxC = 3.6 elseif notch == 2 then if (velocity > 41 and cv == 0) or cv > 41 then vfcCurrent = clamp((cv - velocity) / 3.5, -1.543, 1.543) maxCurrent = vfcCurrent < 0 and -1.543 or 1.543 if math.abs(cv - velocity) > 1.0 then _CONS = true end if math.abs(cv - velocity) < 0.3 then _CONS = false end if not _CONS or cv==0 then vfcCurrent = 0 end else vfcCurrent = 1.03 maxCurrent = 1.03 slipMaxSpdAtMaxC = 24 end elseif notch == 3 then vfcCurrent = 1.543 maxCurrent = 1.543 slipMaxSpdAtMaxC = 37 elseif notch >= 4 then vfcCurrent = 1.543 maxCurrent = 1.543 elseif notch ~= 0 then vfcCurrent = notch / 24 * 1.543 maxCurrent = -clamp(velocity - 0.1, 0, 4.285) if notch == 0 or vfcCurrent > 0 then vfcCurrent = 0; maxCurrent = 0 end end
return vfcCurrent * unitMass * bsk, maxCurrent * unitMass * bsk, slipMaxSpdAtMaxC / bsk^2 end
function transition(a, b, c, d) d = d or c a = math.min(a + c, math.max(a - d, b)) if a ~= a then a = 0 end return a end
function clamp(a, b, c) return math.min(math.max(a, b), c) end
MIN_NUM = 0.0009765625 POWER_EFFECT = 11 BRAKE_EFFECT = 12 _PanV = 0 _Watchdog = false _MI = 0 function onTick() _Watchdog = not _Watchdog
local velocity = math.max(math.abs(input.getNumber(1) * 3.6), MIN_NUM) -- km/h local panV = input.getNumber(4) / 1000 -- kV local pN = input.getNumber(2) -- 0-5 local bN = input.getNumber(3) -- 0-31 local unitM = MASS_M_CAR * input.getNumber(5) -- Mg (t) local cv = input.getNumber(6) * 3.6 -- constant speed km/h local eb = input.getBool(1) local boost = input.getBool(2) local disable_rb = input.getBool(3)
-- voltage safeguard if panV < 1.150 then pN = 0 end if panV < 1.050 then bN = 0 end
panV = panV * LINE_VOLTAGE_LPF + _PanV * (1 - LINE_VOLTAGE_LPF) _PanV = panV
if bN >= 32 or eb then bN = 0; pN = 0 end if bN > 0 then pN = 0 end if disable_rb then bN = 0 end
local motorV = math.max(math.min(velocity * CONST_VF, panV / math.sqrt(2)), MIN_NUM) -- line voltage of motor local vfcI, maxI, slipMaxSpdAtMaxI = TargetCurrent(pN - bN, unitM, velocity, cv, boost)
local min = math.min if vfcI < 0 then min = math.max end
local tgMI = min( maxI / math.max(velocity / math.max(slipMaxSpdAtMaxI, MIN_NUM), 1), -- limit: slip, power vfcI * velocity * CONST_VF / motorV -- constant power ) if vfcI == 0 then tgMI = 0 end _MI = transition(_MI, tgMI, 2)
-- refine rev local i_pRevMaxI = -UNIT_CURRENT_MAX_B * clamp((MAX_LINE_VOLTAGE - panV) / math.max(MAX_LINE_VOLTAGE - REFINE_VOLTAGE, MIN_NUM), 0, 1) local maxRevMI = panV * i_pRevMaxI / (MOTOR_PER_UNIT * math.sqrt(3) * motorV) local resI = 0
if REG_BRAKE then resI = math.max(maxRevMI - _MI, 0) else _MI = math.max(maxRevMI, _MI) end
local trq = MOTOR_PER_UNIT * math.sqrt(3) * motorV * _MI * POWER_EFFECT / (MASS_M_CAR * velocity) local bTrq = math.max( -MOTOR_PER_UNIT * math.sqrt(3) * motorV * tgMI * BRAKE_EFFECT / (MASS_M_CAR * velocity), 0) if bN == 0 then bTrq = 0 end local panI = (_MI - resI) * MOTOR_PER_UNIT * math.sqrt(3) * motorV / math.max(panV, MIN_NUM)
output.setNumber(1, trq / 3.6) -- torque: almost m/s^2 output.setNumber(2, bTrq / 3.6) -- to air brake output.setNumber(3, panI) -- line current output.setNumber(4, _MI) -- current per motor output.setNumber(5, resI) -- resisitor current per motor output.setBool(1, _Watchdog) end

local GRAVITY = {0, -10, 0} local TAU = math.pi * 2
local sin, cos = math.sin, math.cos
local function dot(a, b) return a[1]*b[1] + a[2]*b[2] + a[3]*b[3] end
local function cross(a, b) return { a[2]*b[3] - a[3]*b[2], a[3]*b[1] - a[1]*b[3], a[1]*b[2] - a[2]*b[1] } end
local function add(a, b) return {a[1] + b[1], a[2] + b[2], a[3] + b[3]} end
local function sub(a, b) return {a[1] - b[1], a[2] - b[2], a[3] - b[3]} end
local function mul(a, s) return {a[1]*s, a[2]*s, a[3]*s} end
local function norm(v) return math.sqrt(dot(v, v)) end
local function normalize(v) return mul(v, 1 / norm(v)) end
local function mat3_mul_vec3(M, v) return { M[1]*v[1] + M[2]*v[2] + M[3]*v[3], M[4]*v[1] + M[5]*v[2] + M[6]*v[3], M[7]*v[1] + M[8]*v[2] + M[9]*v[3] } end
local function mat3T_mul_vec3(M, v) return { M[1]*v[1] + M[4]*v[2] + M[7]*v[3], M[2]*v[1] + M[5]*v[2] + M[8]*v[3], M[3]*v[1] + M[6]*v[2] + M[9]*v[3] } end
function apparent_gravity(R, v_local, omega_local, a_local) local omega_world = mat3_mul_vec3(R, omega_local) local a_world = mat3_mul_vec3(R, a_local)
local a_inertial = a_world
local w2 = dot(omega_world, omega_world) if w2 > 1e-10 then local v_world = mat3_mul_vec3(R, v_local) local r_world = mul(cross(omega_world, v_world), -1/w2) local a_centrifugal = cross(omega_world, cross(omega_world, r_world)) a_inertial = add(a_inertial, a_centrifugal) end
return mat3T_mul_vec3(R, sub(GRAVITY, a_inertial)) end
local function rodrigues(axis, s) if dot(axis, axis) < 1e-10 then return { 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, } end axis = normalize(axis)
local c = math.sqrt(1 - s*s) local one_c = 1 - c local ux, uy, uz = axis[1], axis[2], axis[3]
local r00 = c + ux*ux*one_c local r01 = ux*uy*one_c - uz*s local r02 = ux*uz*one_c + uy*s local r10 = uy*ux*one_c + uz*s local r11 = c + uy*uy*one_c local r12 = uy*uz*one_c - ux*s local r20 = uz*ux*one_c - uy*s local r21 = uz*uy*one_c + ux*s local r22 = c + uz*uz*one_c
return { r00, r01, r02, r10, r11, r12, r20, r21, r22, } end

function onTick() local euler_x, euler_y, euler_z = gN(4), gN(5), gN(6) local sx, cx = sin(euler_x), cos(euler_x) local sy, cy = sin(euler_y), cos(euler_y) local sz, cz = sin(euler_z), cos(euler_z) local R = { cy*cz, sx*sy*cz - cx*sz, cx*sy*cz + sx*sz, cy*sz, sx*sy*sz + cx*cz, cx*sy*sz - sx*cz, -sy, sx*cy, cx*cy }

object.script: ins=table.insert function p(s) a={} for e in s:gmatch('[^\n]+')do b={} if e~='-'then for r in e:gmatch('%g*')do c={} for v in r:gmatch('.')do ins(c,tonumber(v,36)) end ins(b,c) end end ins(a,b) end return a end D={{p('z08151 z0611224 z0631131 z061111115 z061123111 z08131 z07153'),0},{p('22 11412111 13111112 11311111 114121'),1}} ANM=property.getNumber('Animation Type') M,S=math,screen gN=input.getNumber T={0,0} I=0 function onTick() T={M.min(gN(1)+1,3)%2-1,gN(1)%3-1} I=gN(3)~=0 and 1 or 0 end t,ta=0,0 function H(x,y,w,r,g,b) a=(1-ta)^2 if ANM==0 then if M.floor(t)<0 then return else a=1 end end S.setColor(r,g,b,255*a) S.drawRectF(x,M.floor(y+0.5),w,1) end function onDraw() for j=1,2 do d=D[j] t=T[j] ta=M.abs(t) if ta<1 then for y,r in ipairs(d[1][I]or{})do x=0 for k,v in ipairs(r)do if k%2==0 then H(24+x,d[2]+y,v,200,200,200)end x=x+v end end end end end

ins=table.insert function p(s) a={} for e in s:gmatch('[^\n]+')do b={} if e~='-'then for r in e:gmatch('%g*')do c={} for v in r:gmatch('.')do ins(c,tonumber(v,36)) end ins(b,c) end end ins(a,b) end return a end D={{p('z041113121z02341 y3431121z21125 x1111121121113z0111132 x11111412121z0214111 x1111111212112z02152 x22111212212z02151 z0112111111111z05131'),55},{p('3232i131d11212 21212131c121k121 21211313221111231221223131112121 24213123124121111112411111112121 2121213121315121111122311111112121 21212141221161111111125111212121'),56}} ANM=property.getNumber('Animation Type') M,S=math,screen C,R=S.setColor,S.drawRectF gN=input.getNumber T={0,0} I=false function onTick() T={M.min(gN(1)+1,3)%2-1,gN(1)%3-1} I=gN(15)~=0 end t,ta=0,0 function tH(x,y,w,r,g,b,a) a=(1-ta)^a if ANM==0 then if M.floor(t)<0 then return else a=1 end end C(r,g,b,255*a) R(x,M.floor(y+0.5),w,1) end function onDraw() if I then C(95,95,95)R(0,55,96,9) for j=1,2 do d=D[j] t=T[j] ta=M.abs(t) if ta<1 then for y,r in ipairs(d[1][1]or{})do x=0 for k,v in ipairs(r)do if k%2==0 then tH(0+x,55+y,v,2,2,2,1)end x=x+v end end end end end end

local cch, sch = property.getNumber"Motor Current Ch.", property.getNumber"Speed Ch." local VOLUME = property.getNumber"VVVF Sound Volume"
local abs, min, max = math.abs, math.min, math.max function onTick() local c, s = input.getNumber(cch), input.getNumber(sch)*3.6 local volume, pitch = {}, {} if abs(c) > 0 then volume[1] = min(min(2.5*s, 0.5), -1*s + 44.5) pitch[1] = 1 if s < 45 then volume[2] = min(0.5*s, 1) end pitch[2] = 1 volume[3] = -0.2*s + 3 pitch[3] = 0.15432*s volume[4] = -0.071429*s + 3.1429 pitch[4] = 0.041667*s if s < 45 then volume[5] = min(0.25*s - 4, 1) end pitch[5] = 0.027778*s if 45 <= s then volume[6] = min(1, -0.1*s + 6) end pitch[6] = 0.019183*s if 45 <= s then volume[7] = min(1, -0.05*s + 5.25) end pitch[7] = 0.013889*s volume[8] = 0.05*s - 3.5 pitch[8] = 0.0086806*s end for i = 1, 8 do output.setNumber(2*i - 1, min(max((volume[i] or 0)*VOLUME, 0), 1)) output.setNumber(2*i, max(pitch[i] or 0, 0)) end end

local sch = property.getNumber"Speed Ch." local RUNNING_SOUND_INDICES = {} for s in (property.getText"Running Sound"):gmatch("([^,]+)") do table.insert(RUNNING_SOUND_INDICES, tonumber(s)) end
function onTick() local speed = input.getNumber(sch) local volume = speed*3.6/60 for _, i in ipairs(RUNNING_SOUND_INDICES) do output.setNumber(2*i - 1, volume) output.setNumber(2*i, speed) end end
